strings: <voice_0x01000E38><se_high>Dye: Why don't you show me that ugly face again? Je ;;; I said I had nothing to say.
<voice_0x01000E39><se_high>Dye: What do you do now? Don't tell me that you came to see me!
<voice_0x01000E3A><se_low>January: No just go. Only the captain knows the age of that ship...
<voice_0x01000E3B><se_high>Dye: I'm here to show off, give me the lemon! You can hold your breath because you have my boat.
<voice_0x01000E3C><se_high>Dye: I'd love to show you if I could, but I can't right now. It's a shame because these ships are of high quality. She calls herself a pretty woman.
<voice_0x01000E3D><se_low>January: ... don't fall, don't fall! Gordon Bennett How did we get here?!
